title: All aboard for Sea Tech Week 2022 - ANI News
content: All aboard for Sea Tech Week 2022  ANI News
description: New Delhi [India] April 21 (ANI/PRNewswire): India is the country of honour for the Sea Tech Week® and will be making waves from September 26-30, 2022 at Brest Expo, France. Registration is now open for visitors and exhibitors. Avail the Early Bird before May 31.
